13. Terraform (iac automation tool) (15/20 days)
	1. iac architecture
	2. terraform architecture
	3. terraform modules
	4. terraform plugin
	5. terraform scripts
	6. terraform remote state file management
	7. terraform provisioners
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

14. Jenkins (Continous Integration Server) (15/20 days)
	1. What is Continous Integration and Continous deployment/delivery means, how this can be achieved?
	2. ci/cd tools available in the market
	3. Jenkins architecture
	4. Setting up the Jenkins cluster
	5. Adding and configuring jenkins agent Nodes
	6. Global Tool configurations
	7. Plugin management
		1. GIT
		2. MAVEN
		3. ANSIBLE
		4. TERRAFORM
		5. JDK
	8. Jenkins Secrets
	9. Jenkins Job
		1. Free-style
		2. Pipeline Job
			2.1 declarative pipeline (plugins with shellscripting)
			2.2 scripted pipeline (groovy script knowledge)
	10 jenkins parameters (static/dynamic)
	11. creating a pipeline job with terraform, ansible integration for delivering e2e application on the aws cloud
	
15. Docker (25/30 days)
	1. What is containerization?
	2. Virtualization vs Containerization
	3. How does containerization technology works?
		1. linux namespaces
		2. cgroups
		3. union filesystem
	4. docker vs open container specification (runc)
	5. docker registry
	6. docker image (layered / stackable)
	7. docker context
	8. docker workflow (command-line interface commands) (image/container management)
	9. docker directives
		1. image management directives
			1. ENV
			2. FROM
			3. ADD
			4. COPY
			5. RUN
			6. EXPOSE
			7. VOLUME
			8. WORKDIR
			9. LABEL
		2. container management directivies
			1. CMD
			2. ENTRYPOINT
	10. how to run the docker container as?
		1. interactive
		2. infinite
	11. docker volumes
		1. bind mounts
		2. bind volumes
	12. docker networking
	13. docker compose

16. Kubernetes (20/25 days)
	1. Container Cluster Manager, why do we need?
	2. Kubernetes Architecture
	3. Installing and configuring the Kubernetes cluster
		1. docker-desktop kubernetes
		2. eks cluster (aws cloudplatform)
		3. minicube
  4. kubectl and kubeconfig
	5. kubernetes objects
	6. kubernetes namespaces
	7. kubectl cli commands
	8. kubernetes controllers
		1. DaemonSet
		2. DeploymentSet
		3. ReplicaSet
		4. Job
		5. Service
			1. ClusterIP
			2. NodePort
			3. LoadBalancer
			4. Ingress
			5. Headless Service
 9. Kubernetes ConfigMaps
